data.description: This is a great home for the young family. Large kitchen with all appliances and abundant dining area, so the family can eat together.  Large walk-in pantry.  Huge living room with attractive gas log fireplace.  Main floor has powder rm. & Laundry rm. Upstairs features an open stairway. 2 bedrooms & M.B & master bath with jacuzzi tub,  shower, + another full bath.  Full basement & Vinyl fencing. The property is being marketed in as/is condition with no inspections provided by the owner
